Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:51.35,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoberiem ho do vesmíru, a odpálim to tam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:10.52,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime stúpa spoločne s Ostrumom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:15.64,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,Aktivácia odpočítavania Typu-X bola potvrdená.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:17.96,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,180 sekúnd do detonácie!
