Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.84,0:19:37.80,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,To nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:46.33,Dragon,,0000,0000,0000,,To je zlé! Upustila Typ-X!
